verbose_text: The influence of naringenin on the steroidogenic enzyme levels were investigated, and in the rat model of PCOS treated with letrozole (Group III), there was an increase in the levels of both 3beta-hydroxysteroid dehydrogenase (3beta-HSD) and 17beta-hydroxysteroid dehydrogenase (17beta-HSD) when compared with the controls (Group I and Group II).
evidence: levels of both 3beta-hydroxysteroid dehydrogenase (3beta-HSD) and 17beta-hydroxysteroid dehydrogenase
